
  career-ops dashboard

  → http://localhost:4280/

  Endpoints:
    GET  /                  dashboard (auto-regenerates)
    GET  /tmp/runs/...      run artefacts (cv.pdf, screenshots, jd.md)
    GET  /api/status        JSON list of runs + stages
    POST /api/status        { slug, stage, note? } update status.yml
    POST /api/regen         force regenerate dashboard.html

  Press Ctrl+C to stop.


